 the Gaon Digital Chart, but appeared at number 63 on the component Download chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=06&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|script-title=ko:2020\ub144 06\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart|trans-title=Week 6 of 2020 Download Chart|date=February 2\u20138, 2020|website=Gaon Music Chart|accessdate=February 12, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>}} || 85 || 61 || 3\n| \n* US: 1,000<ref name=\"Reminiscencebillboard\"/>\n| ''Reminiscence''\n|-\n| colspan=\"9\" style=\"font-size:80%;\" | \"\u2014\" denotes items that did not chart or were not released in that region.\n|}\n\n===Other charted songs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sales \n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Billboard charts#International charts|US<br>World]]<br><ref name=\"wdt\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |\"Hush\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n| 8\n|\n* US: 1,000<ref name=\"adios\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Hush''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |\"You Don't Know Me\"\n| 10\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"font-size:80%;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes items that did not chart or were not released in that region.\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n===Reality shows===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center; table-layout:fixed; margin-right:0\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Network \n! Title\n! Episodes\n! Note\n|-\n| 2019\n| [[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]]'s M2\n| ''Everglow Land''\n| 5\n| First broadcast August 13<ref>{{cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/now/article/109/0004059076|title='\ub300\uc138 \ub8e8\ud0a4' \uc5d0\ubc84\uae00\ub85c\uc6b0, M2\uc11c \uccab \ub9ac\uc5bc\ub9ac\ud2f0 \ub860\uce6d..8\uc6d4 13\uc77c \uccab\ubc29 [\uacf5\uc2dd]|date=July 31, 2019|website=Naver|language=ko