70710150246/https://www.raf.mod.uk/rafcms/mediafiles/E28BE76F_5056_A318_A833EB4C9A735AD8.pdf#page=44|archive-date=10 July 2017|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=Tactical_Hearing_Protection_System_(THPS)_User_Information>{{cite web |author=Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom) |title = Tactical Hearing Protection System (THPS) User Information |year= |url= http://www.army.mod.uk/documents/general/Tactical_hearing.pdf |accessdate= 14 October 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014233713/http://www.army.mod.uk/documents/general/Tactical_hearing.pdf|archive-date=14 October 2017|author-link = Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom) }}</ref> ''17T'' (''L132A1''), ''19'' (''L137A1'')<ref name=Tactical_Hearing_Protection_System_(THPS)_User_Information/>\n|-\n| [[Specialist Firearms Command]] of the [[Metropolitan Police Service]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.met.police.uk/co19/armed_response.htm |title=Metropolitan Police Service&nbsp;\u2013 Central Operations, Specialist Firearms unit (CO19) |publisher=Met.police.uk |accessdate=2009-07-24 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905024146/http://www.met.police.uk/co19/armed_response.htm |archivedate=2009-09-05 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''17'', ''26''<ref>{{cite web|title=Timesonline.co.uk|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/politics/article7149078.ece |accessdate=June 12, 2010 }}{{dead link|date=May 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Police Service of Northern Ireland]];<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.u.tv/News/New-guns-to-be-issued-to-PSNI/0ffe9630-0fec-4129-9708-0b4fdcbbbbd4 |title=New guns to be issued to PSNI |publisher=UTV News |date=2002-10-25 |accessdate=2010-06-29 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725010743/http://www.u.tv/News/New-guns-to-be-issued-to-PSNI/0ffe9630-0fec-4129-9708-0b4fdcbbbbd4 |archivedate=2011-07-25 }}</ref> [[Police Scotland#Armed Policing|Police Scotland]] Specialist Firearms Units<ref>